                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Choosing Colombia is a statement of style and substance. It is an immersion into a culture that pulses with infectious alegría (joy) and offers a breathtaking gallery of backdrops that feel pulled from the pages of magical realism:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                             <span class="text-[#D1C1A3] mt-1">•</span>
                             <span>The sun-drenched, historic fortifications of <a href="#" class="text-[#4EAC9F] underline font-medium">Cartagena</a>.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                             <span class="text-[#D1C1A3] mt-1">•</span>
                             <span>The lush, eternally spring-like mountains of <a href="#" class="text-[#4EAC9F] underline font-medium">Medellín</a>.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                             <span class="text-[#D1C1A3] mt-1">•</span>
                             <span>The unparalleled biodiversity and serenity of the <a href="#" class="text-[#4EAC9F] underline font-medium">Coffee Cultural Landscape</a>.</span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
