                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-6 text-sm md:text-base">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <span class="text-[#4EAC9F] mt-1">•</span>
                            <span><strong class="text-[#4EAC9F]">Legally Binding & Globally Recognized:</strong> A Colombian marriage certificate is fully valid in countries with marriage equality, including the US, Canada, the UK, and most of Europe.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <span class="text-[#4EAC9F] mt-1">•</span>
                            <span><strong class="text-[#4EAC9F]">Accessible for International Couples:</strong> You do not need to be a resident. The transparent process allows foreign nationals to enter a valid civil union with ease.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
