                            <span class="text-[#4EAC9F] mt-1">•</span>
                            <span><strong class="text-[#4EAC9F]">Why it's Perfect for LGBTQ+ Weddings:</strong> As a global tourism hub, Cartagena is cosmopolitan and sophisticated. Its luxury infrastructure is the most developed in the country, ensuring world-class service.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <span class="text-[#4EAC9F] mt-1">•</span>
                            <span><strong class="text-[#4EAC9F]">Iconic Venues:</strong></span>
