                        <li class="pl-6 italic text-[#333638] space-y-4">
                            <p><strong class="not-italic">Colonial Mansions:</strong> Host an intimate reception in a private courtyard, surrounded by stone arches and balconies dripping with fuchsia bougainvillea.</p>
                            <p><strong class="not-italic">Historic Baluartes (City Walls):</strong> Exchange vows atop the ancient city walls as the sun sets over the Caribbean Sea—a truly cinematic experience.</p>
                            <p><strong class="not-italic">Private Islands (Barú & Rosario Islands):</strong> For the ultimate in exclusivity. A white-sand beachfront ceremony followed by a non-stop party in your own private paradise.</p>
