                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                            <span class="text-[#4EAC9F] mt-1">•</span>
                            <span><strong class="text-[#4EAC9F]">The Coffee Axis:</strong> Imagine saying "I do" at a luxury coffee plantation (hacienda), your ceremony overlooking the rolling green hills and towering wax palms of the Cocora Valley. This is the definition of "quiet luxury"—sophisticated, serene, and organic.</span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
